    <item>
      <title>陪审团获悉，鲍勃·梅内德斯敦促美国官员“停止干涉”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/bob-menendez-urged-us-official-to-stop-interfering-jury-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国农业部一名前官员作证称，参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯 (Bob Menendez) 于 2019 年告诉他“不要再干涉”一名获得埃及垄断权的选民对美国肉类出口进行认证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/bob-menendez-urged-us-official-to-stop-interfering-jury-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型民意调查显示英国保守党将遭遇历史性失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/uk-tories-on-course-for-historic-defeat-according-to-mega-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五发布的一项大样本详细民意调查显示，英国工党有望获得压倒性胜利，这可能会导致执政的保守党失去四分之三以上的席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/uk-tories-on-course-for-historic-defeat-according-to-mega-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国保守党承诺在激烈竞争中增加城镇资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/tories-pledge-funding-boost-for-towns-in-closely-fought-uk-races</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党承诺为英国城镇提供 6 亿英镑（7.64 亿美元）的资金，其中包括该党此前与工党和苏格兰民族党激烈角逐的多个席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/tories-pledge-funding-boost-for-towns-in-closely-fought-uk-races</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
